## Pitfall #2: Not Handling Rate Limits

### ❌ Anti-Pattern
```typescript
// Blast requests, crash on 429
for (const item of items) {
  await {{ company }}Client.process(item);  // Will hit rate limit
}
```

### ✅ Better Approach
```typescript
import pLimit from 'p-limit';

const limit = pLimit(5);  // Max 5 concurrent
const rateLimiter = new RateLimiter({ tokensPerSecond: 10 });

for (const item of items) {
  await rateLimiter.acquire();
  await limit(() => {{ company }}Client.process(item));
}
```

