## Pitfall #5: Not Validating Webhooks

### ❌ Anti-Pattern
```typescript
// Trust any incoming request
app.post('/webhook', (req, res) => {
  processWebhook(req.body);  // Attacker can send fake events
  res.sendStatus(200);
});
```

### ✅ Better Approach
```typescript
app.post('/webhook',
  express.raw({ type: 'application/json' }),
  (req, res) => {
    const signature = req.headers['x-{{ company }}-signature'];
    if (!verify{{ display_name }}Signature(req.body, signature)) {
      return res.sendStatus(401);
    }
    processWebhook(JSON.parse(req.body));
    res.sendStatus(200);
  }
);
```

