## Pitfall #8: Not Implementing Circuit Breaker

### ❌ Anti-Pattern
```typescript
// When {{ display_name }} is down, every request hangs
for (const user of users) {
  await {{ company }}Client.sync(user);  // All timeout sequentially
}
```

### ✅ Better Approach
```typescript
import CircuitBreaker from 'opossum';

const breaker = new CircuitBreaker({{ company }}Client.sync, {
  timeout: 10000,
  errorThresholdPercentage: 50,
  resetTimeout: 30000,
});

// Fails fast when circuit is open
for (const user of users) {
  await breaker.fire(user).catch(handleFailure);
}
```

